1
00:01:08,769 --> 00:01:11,602
阿者言无 鼻者名间 为无时间
Avici Hell. Also known as Continuous Hell.

2
00:01:12,036 --> 00:01:16,200
为无空间 为无量受业报之界
Uninterrupted Time. Unlimited Space. Boundless suffering for the fallen souls.

3
00:01:17,571 --> 00:01:20,131
无时间
Uninterrupted Time

4
00:01:21,471 --> 00:01:23,471
{\an8}(时间)
(Time)

5
00:01:22,675 --> 00:01:25,365
我还记得我第一次抓那个犯人
I still remember my first arrest.

6
00:01:26,674 --> 00:01:28,474
{\an8}(1991年)
(1991)

7
00:01:28,473 --> 00:01:30,805
那天是八零年十二月十二日
It was December 12, 1980.

8
00:01:34,341 --> 00:01:36,673
我跟一个师兄在河内道巡逻
My partner and I were patrolling Hanoi Road.

9
00:01:36,715 --> 00:01:41,076
那么收到通知 说新世界有案件发生
Shit was going down at New World Centre.

10
00:01:41,343 --> 00:01:43,140
我们俩立刻赶去
We rushed over.

11
00:01:43,643 --> 00:01:46,584
到了现场 看见几十个人挥舞刀棍正在械斗
A gang fight was taking place.

12
00:01:46,585 --> 00:01:49,772
有十几个已经倒在地上
About 15 or so were already down.

13
00:01:50,744 --> 00:01:52,268
地上有好多血
Lots of blood on the ground.

14
00:01:53,945 --> 00:01:56,436
我更看见一只握了刀的断手
Plus a severed hand, still holding a knife.

15
00:02:01,913 --> 00:02:03,676
师兄叫我开枪
My partner told me to draw my weapon.

16
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:08,546
当时我是个新丁 师兄说什么我就做什么 是吧!
I was a rookie so I did what he told me to.

17
00:02:09,262 --> 00:02:11,329
谁知道我还没来得及打开枪套呢
But before I could open the holster,

18
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:15,379
师兄已经"扑通" 跌倒在我面前了
My partner already dropped

19
00:02:16,283 --> 00:02:20,652
我看见那小子拿根铁管插进师兄的肚子里
This kid stabbed a pipe into his belly

20
00:02:21,751 --> 00:02:24,982
那血呢 就不停从那里面流出来
Blood gushed out of the sawed-off opening

21
00:02:26,685 --> 00:02:28,269
当时我的脑袋一片空白
I didn't know what to think.

22
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:30,155
只知道把六颗子弹
I simply emptied all six of my bullets 

23
00:02:30,156 --> 00:02:32,983
一下子全打在那小子的身上
straight into that kid.

24
00:02:35,354 --> 00:02:37,879
后来那小子判了多少年我记的不大清楚
I don't remember how many years he got.

25
00:02:39,754 --> 00:02:42,075
两年前 我又遇上那小子了
But when I saw him again two years ago,

26
00:02:42,076 --> 00:02:46,277
穿的衣着光鲜 跟一伙人在富豪喝酒
he was boozing in a club, looking sharp.

27
00:02:46,278 --> 00:02:50,616
跟着一块的那几个人呢 就是倪坤的手下
His buddies were all Kwun's goons!

28
00:02:54,557 --> 00:02:59,517
杀人放火金腰带 修桥补路无尸骸
Evil prevails. Only the good die young.

29
00:03:05,859 --> 00:03:08,453
那个师兄长什么样子我已经很模糊了
I can barely recall my partner's face now.

30
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,384
我很后悔
I regret...

31
00:03:11,523 --> 00:03:15,395
那六枪没打在那小子的头上
the six bullets weren't put into that kid's skull.

32
00:03:21,161 --> 00:03:23,425
世界不应该是这样
The world shouldn't be like this.

33
00:03:25,163 --> 00:03:27,188
做人不应该是这样 琛
That's not the way it should be, Sam.

34
00:03:33,733 --> 00:03:35,864
你来尖沙嘴多久?
How long have you been around Tsim Sha Tsui?

35
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:38,793
快两年了吧
Almost two years now.

36
00:03:42,101 --> 00:03:44,228
你知不知道这两年来我为什么没有抓你?
Do you know why I haven't messed with you?

37
00:03:45,004 --> 00:03:46,625
我长得帅吧
'Cause I'm handsome.

38
00:03:48,268 --> 00:03:49,701
可能是吧
Maybe so.

39
00:03:50,774 --> 00:03:53,572
因为我觉得你还像个人
'Cause I think you 're a decent guy.

40
00:03:55,510 --> 00:03:59,877
如果尖沙嘴是你的地头 我就清闲多了
I'd rather you be in charge in Tsim Sha Tsui.

41
00:03:59,878 --> 00:04:01,411
算了吧
Forget about it.

42
00:04:01,412 --> 00:04:03,735
六颗子弹都没打死那小子
You couldn't waste the kid even with six bullets.

43
00:04:04,171 --> 00:04:05,638
你也算是个好人 对吧?
That makes you a decent guy, too. Right?

44
00:04:06,605 --> 00:04:10,837
别笑话我了 这个好人我宁愿不做
Let me put it this way. I'd rather not be one.

45
00:04:18,041 --> 00:04:21,010
我这条命 是坤哥给我的
Kwun gave me everything, even my life.

46
00:04:21,942 --> 00:04:25,355
我要是帮你对付他 我还算是个人吗?
If I turned against him

47
00:04:25,356 --> 00:04:28,443
你也会看不起我吧 对不对?
I'd be despicable even in your eyes. Right?

48
00:04:29,991 --> 00:04:34,637
- 早就料到你是这样 - 本来就是嘛
- I knew you 'd say that. - Yeah!

49
00:04:35,011 --> 00:04:39,038
不过为倪家做事呢 不能只讲义气
Chivalry means little to the Ngai's Family

50
00:04:44,713 --> 00:04:46,476
师傅常常告诫我
The Master often says...

51
00:04:47,514 --> 00:04:50,176
因果报应总有时
"Retribution knows its time."

52
00:04:52,315 --> 00:04:55,751
我也害怕最后几年不能和你吃饭
Who knows how you and I will end up?

53
00:04:59,071 --> 00:05:00,808
开工了
Time to work.

54
00:05:02,217 --> 00:05:04,405
还早呢 这么拼命干什么?
This early? What's the rush?

55
00:05:04,406 --> 00:05:06,073
我不吃 小的也要吃啊
I've got to eat. So do my boys.

56
00:05:06,074 --> 00:05:08,351
全都拿走吧 还有这个
Take the whole box.

57
00:05:08,585 --> 00:05:09,207
不要了 留给你吧
That's okay. Keep it.

58
00:05:09,208 --> 00:05:12,006
不用了 走吧
Don't worry about it. Just go.

59
00:05:12,876 --> 00:05:13,865
走了
Gotta go.

60
00:05:19,613 --> 00:05:21,911
要不要带你走后门?
Want to use the back door?

61
00:05:22,855 --> 00:05:25,722
条例没规定不许跟警察做朋友吧
Ain't no rules against schmoozing with cops.

62
00:05:26,455 --> 00:05:28,446
走正门行了 习惯了
The front door's fine. Got used to it.

63
00:05:45,359 --> 00:05:46,121
宝勒巷
Prat Avenue!

64
00:06:08,097 --> 00:06:09,496
宝勒巷 劳驾
Prat Avenue, please.

65
00:07:39,215 --> 00:07:40,341
我找坤叔
Is Uncle Kwun in?

66
00:07:42,183 --> 00:07:43,980
坤叔 有人找你
Uncle Kwun! Someone's looking for you .

67
00:08:40,402 --> 00:08:42,088
我走了 Mary姐
Bye, Mary.

68
00:08:57,265 --> 00:08:58,994
这部美国古董机
They say this American antique's got

69
00:08:59,232 --> 00:09:03,396
有人说它高音甜 中音准 低音劲什么的
a sweet high, crisp middle, and strong bass.

70
00:09:04,066 --> 00:09:05,761
真是瞎扯蛋
Bullshit!

71
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,731
要十八万呢
180 grand!

72
00:09:07,934 --> 00:09:10,129
香港有多少人买得起?
Who can afford it in Hong Kong?

73
00:09:10,768 --> 00:09:11,735
坐
Sit.

74
00:09:15,803 --> 00:09:18,499
玩得起的人有一万多
Only around ten thousand people can afford it

75
00:09:18,736 --> 00:09:20,829
琛哥叫你去警察那边做卧底
Sam asked you to be a mole in the force.

76
00:09:21,603 --> 00:09:24,253
你要是不喜欢 我去跟他说一声
If you don't like it, I can talk to him.

77
00:09:24,254 --> 00:09:26,620
怎么说你也是我的人
You're my boy after all

78
00:09:29,005 --> 00:09:29,937
没事
It's fine with me.

79
00:09:31,405 --> 00:09:32,394
真的没事?
Sure?

80
00:09:34,239 --> 00:09:35,365
真的
Positive.

81
00:09:38,474 --> 00:09:39,600
帮我把那个袋子拿过来
Hand me that bag.

82
00:09:43,063 --> 00:09:44,700
玛莉姐
Mary.

83
00:09:46,875 --> 00:09:50,276
我看你最近无精打采的 还以为你不想去呢
I thought you'd been dreading it

84
00:09:51,376 --> 00:09:54,470
这几天风声紧 回屯门蹲一段时间吧
Hide in Tuen Mun till things quiet down.

85
00:09:55,143 --> 00:09:57,202
炼好身体等警察学校开学
Stay fit for the Academy's new term.

86
00:10:00,344 --> 00:10:03,142
给你这笔钱 省着点用
The money I gave you, spend wisely.

87
00:10:06,612 --> 00:10:08,079
喜欢这首歌?
You like the song?

88
00:10:10,046 --> 00:10:11,138
是啊
Yeah.

89
00:10:16,514 --> 00:10:17,776
送给你
It's yours.

90
00:10:18,549 --> 00:10:21,109
但是用别的机子放 效果差很远
It won't sound as good on another player.

91
00:10:22,183 --> 00:10:24,981
以后赚到钱 我给你找一部好的
Someday I'll pick out a good one for you

92
00:10:26,848 --> 00:10:29,409
怎么 不喜欢?
What? Don't like it?

93
00:10:31,318 --> 00:10:32,478
不是
Not at all.

94
00:10:32,884 --> 00:10:34,613
这表 琛哥送给你的?
Sam gave you this watch, didn't he?

95
00:10:35,218 --> 00:10:36,412
不关你事
None of your business.

96
00:10:43,253 --> 00:10:44,515
今天晚上的事
Only you and I...

97
00:10:45,554 --> 00:10:46,919
只有你和我知道
...know about tonight.

98
00:10:47,787 --> 00:10:49,084
我不想琛哥知道
I don't want Sam to know.

99
00:10:49,593 --> 00:10:51,219
为什么?
Why's that?

100
00:10:52,888 --> 00:10:54,617
做女人很简单
Women are simple.

101
00:10:55,689 --> 00:10:59,420
只要男人好 我做什么都行
A man treats me well, I'd do anything.

102
00:11:01,623 --> 00:11:05,115
你先回去吧 我今天晚上会很忙
Now go home. I'm very busy tonight.

103
00:11:16,904 --> 00:11:22,073
没什么的 出来混 不是你扁我就是我扁你
It's either you or me.

104
00:11:22,074 --> 00:11:25,688
师傅说我今天有血光之灾 我知道
The boss predicted I would get hurt today.

105
00:11:26,162 --> 00:11:31,156
那又怎么样?表叔看得起我 老是问我
The Mainlander kept asking...

106
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:33,725
强哥 今天有没有奔驰啊?
"Got a Mercedes today, Keung?"

107
00:11:33,897 --> 00:11:35,831
我当然说有了 所以就出事了
I said, "Of course." And here I am!

108
00:11:36,765 --> 00:11:40,360
要不然 我用得着对着你?
Otherwise, I wouldn't be here with you .

109
00:11:40,432 --> 00:11:43,731
我啊 早就在中国城搂着妹妹 享受大餐了
Mainland girls in arms.

110
00:11:44,033 --> 00:11:45,967
还用说?
That's for sure!

111
00:11:51,301 --> 00:11:53,895
哎 来根烟抽抽啊
Hey, got a cigarette?

112
00:11:55,602 --> 00:11:56,694
我不抽烟的
I don't smoke.

113
00:12:11,805 --> 00:12:14,069
我看算了吧 我的车也没事
Let's forget about it. My car's fine.

114
00:12:14,372 --> 00:12:16,738
就是嘛 事主都说没事了
See! She says it's all good

115
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:20,540
没什么的 你看看你
Dressed all dandy.

116
00:12:20,841 --> 00:12:24,208
穿的那么斯文 当然不想多事了
Don't want any trouble, do you?

117
00:12:24,707 --> 00:12:27,471
你看我 给你打的
Look at me. All beaten up by you.

118
00:12:27,808 --> 00:12:31,471
你说 到了法庭法官信谁?你自己想想
Who do you think the judge would believe?

119
00:12:32,275 --> 00:12:35,711
还有啊 你们不去尖东吗?
I bet you guys never go to Tsim Sha Tsui East, huh?

120
00:12:35,944 --> 00:12:38,172
你知道我是谁呀?我是傻强
Know who I am? I'm Keung!

121
00:12:38,173 --> 00:12:41,337
韩琛的头马 迪路的头马
Sam's top dog. Del Piero's boy.

122
00:12:41,611 --> 00:12:43,875
怎么样?当然见你一次打你一次
I'll kick your ass every time I see you.

123
00:12:43,876 --> 00:12:45,276
还用说?
And you can count on that.

124
00:13:05,819 --> 00:13:06,843
诶
Hey,you .

125
00:13:07,217 --> 00:13:09,287
警官 我看叫救护车吧
How about calling an ambulance, sir?

126
00:13:09,288 --> 00:13:11,483
你看 流血了都
Look at all the blood!

127
00:13:11,817 --> 00:13:14,081
叫他们多准备500毫升O型血 很难找的
Have them bring 500 cc Type O. It's rare!

128
00:13:14,418 --> 00:13:15,476
O什么O?
Shut up!

129
00:13:15,751 --> 00:13:17,651
跟我回警局再慢慢解释
Wait till we're back to the station

130
00:13:18,058 --> 00:13:20,824
- 带走! - 喂 为什么要我去警局?
- Take him. - Why do I have to go to the station?

131
00:13:20,825 --> 00:13:23,660
喂 现在车又没丢 干么要我上警局?
I only stole a piece of junk, sir. What've I done to deserve the OCTB?

132
00:13:23,661 --> 00:13:26,511
- 闭嘴吧!还说! - 喂!跟你们回去 还不是让你们扁?
- Just shut up! - Does that deserve an OCTB beating?

133
00:13:26,653 --> 00:13:28,416
知不知道你只是个学警?
Don't you know you're just a cadet?

134
00:13:29,287 --> 00:13:31,414
还说今年想拿全班第一呢?
And you are expected to get a medal this year?

135
00:13:31,797 --> 00:13:33,924
别让叶长官知道
Don't ever let Yip know about this!

136
00:13:45,557 --> 00:13:46,785
叶长官 生日快乐
Happy birthday, Officer Yip.

137
00:13:47,124 --> 00:13:48,989
什么快乐?
What's there to be happy about?

138
00:13:49,592 --> 00:13:53,399
在警校蹲了十年 见树比见人还多
Ten years in the Academy. A rustic hell.

139
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,559
你都能把我弄出去
You even managed to get me out.

140
00:13:57,727 --> 00:13:59,456
你的案子已经隔了那么长时间
Your case is now ancient history.

141
00:13:59,727 --> 00:14:02,423
想一想 把自己也申调出去算了
Get yourself out.

142
00:14:04,761 --> 00:14:07,211
虽然现在由华人担任处长
So what if the Commissioner is Chinese now?

143
00:14:07,212 --> 00:14:10,323
但要等老外都走了 还要六年
Still six more years till the hand-over.

144
00:14:10,662 --> 00:14:12,562
那时候我四十八了
I'll be 48 by then.

145
00:14:13,964 --> 00:14:18,867
不如在学校 多教几个好警察
Might as well train a few good cops here.

146
00:14:18,985 --> 00:14:21,756
九七后看你们的了
The world is yours after 1997!

147
00:14:23,866 --> 00:14:25,766
27149 干杯...
27149! Cheers!

148
00:14:26,221 --> 00:14:28,230
阿仁
Yan.

149
00:14:28,399 --> 00:14:29,559
响了一整天了
Been beeping the whole day,

150
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:30,528
怎么不回电话?
How come you don't call back?

151
00:14:30,766 --> 00:14:31,824
女朋友?
Girlfriend?

152
00:14:32,968 --> 00:14:34,367
干杯 长官 干杯...
Cheers, sir!  Cheers!

153
00:14:35,034 --> 00:14:36,092
滚啊
Just leave me alone!

154
00:14:36,368 --> 00:14:37,528
不关我的事 我也不想知道
It's none of my business. I don't want to know a thing.

155
00:14:37,702 --> 00:14:39,033
滚!滚啊!
Go! Leave me alone!

156
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:46,037
罗继
Law.

157
00:14:47,170 --> 00:14:48,137
你干什么?
What do you want?

158
00:14:49,804 --> 00:14:51,237
我爸爸刚去世
My father just passed way.

159
00:14:56,472 --> 00:14:58,201
他生前曾经吩咐过
It was his wish to inform his children...

160
00:14:59,472 --> 00:15:02,032
如果他出事的话 就要通知所有的子女
...when something bad happened to him.

161
00:15:04,974 --> 00:15:06,407
不好意思 打扰了
Sorry to have bothered you!

162
00:15:28,845 --> 00:15:31,682
黑鬼 看什么电视 先吃饭吧
Stop watching TV! Eatfirst, Negro!

163
00:15:31,683 --> 00:15:36,049
坤叔走了 看电视台有什么消息
I wonder what they have on Kwun's death.

164
00:15:37,019 --> 00:15:38,672
文拯 这事你干的?
Did you do it, Ching?

165
00:15:40,047 --> 00:15:41,878
我嘴巴大 要是我干的
I've got a big mouth. Had I done it...

166
00:15:42,115 --> 00:15:43,275
早就通天啦
...you would've heard about it!

167
00:15:43,515 --> 00:15:44,607
你问问国华 甘地
Ask Wah and Gandhi.

168
00:15:44,923 --> 00:15:48,490
哎 那就糟了 坤叔死的时候
When Kwun died, I was in Macau.

169
00:15:48,491 --> 00:15:50,782
我正在澳门谈生意
Everybody knows!

170
00:15:50,783 --> 00:15:52,659
这回 他的子女一定算在我头上
But I bet his kids think I did it.

171
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:55,308
- 我甘地怕什么呀! - 就是
- I ain't scared of nothing - Right.

172
00:15:55,484 --> 00:15:57,952
大儿子当医生 小儿子游手好闲
The eldest son's a doctor. The youngest a brat.

173
00:15:58,252 --> 00:15:59,276
女儿嫁人了
The daughter's been married for ages.

174
00:15:59,519 --> 00:16:01,612
只剩下二儿子看着他的生意
Only the middle son's running the show.

175
00:16:01,886 --> 00:16:06,255
如果他们太过份 我随时收拾他们
If they go too far, I'll show them!

176
00:16:06,419 --> 00:16:08,319
没保护好坤叔 是我们不好
We failed to protect Kwun. It's ourfault!

177
00:16:09,354 --> 00:16:11,286
三叔 算了
That's enough, Uncle John.

178
00:16:11,487 --> 00:16:13,045
爸爸常说
Dad used to say...

179
00:16:13,888 --> 00:16:16,220
"出来跑 迟早要还的"
"What goes around comes around."

180
00:16:17,256 --> 00:16:20,248
他现在才出事 算是赚了
It came later than expected already.

181
00:16:22,090 --> 00:16:24,615
你们谁能猜到 国华 文拯...
Wah, Ching, Negro and Gandhi.

182
00:16:25,023 --> 00:16:28,642
黑鬼 甘地他们四个 现在想什么?
Guess what those four are thinking?

183
00:16:31,525 --> 00:16:33,425
麻烦你们 谢谢
Thank you . Thank you all.

184
00:16:36,459 --> 00:16:39,485
姐 妈妈怎么样?没事吧?
How's mom doing, sis?

185
00:16:40,126 --> 00:16:42,151
没事 一早睡着了
She's fine. Been sleeping.

186
00:16:42,894 --> 00:16:46,416
她吩咐 买几包香烟送去殓房给爸爸
She wants us to bring some cigs to the morgue for Dad.

187
00:16:46,417 --> 00:16:48,050
我去买
I'll go get them.

188
00:16:54,963 --> 00:16:57,864
B组负责把守德诚街两边的街口
B Team, watch Tak Shing Street.

189
00:16:58,130 --> 00:17:00,758
C组呢 把守财务公司那幢大厦
C Team, watch the Austin Road exit...

190
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,195
在柯士甸道这边的出入口
...of thatfinancial building

191
00:17:03,436 --> 00:17:04,733
这幢大厦有两个出入口
It has two exits

192
00:17:04,971 --> 00:17:06,666
一个在德诚街 一个在柯...
One on Tak Shing Street. One on Austin...

193
00:17:06,939 --> 00:17:07,871
对不起
Sorry.

194
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,230
喂?
Hello?

195
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,695
倪坤死了这么大的事 你为什么不告诉我?
Why didn't you call me that Kwun was dead?

196
00:17:15,696 --> 00:17:18,859
一出事我就通知所有人了 大哥
I called everybody the minute it happened!

197
00:17:19,068 --> 00:17:20,899
倪坤一死 下面的肯定坐不住
Kwun's boys can't sit still for sure

198
00:17:21,135 --> 00:17:22,625
今晚尖沙嘴呀 准有事发生
Shit will hit the fan in Tsim Sha Tsui tonight.

199
00:17:22,935 --> 00:17:23,899
你不知道 今天十四号
<i>It's the 14th already. You know that?</i>

200
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:27,764
今天十四号 大家都要向倪家交钱
The 14th. Time to pay the Ngai Family

201
00:17:29,236 --> 00:17:31,670
这里我最小
I'm the junior partner here.

202
00:17:31,870 --> 00:17:33,428
不好听的话我来说
So let me be the jackass.

203
00:17:34,238 --> 00:17:37,036
这个月起 我不再交钱给坤叔啦
I'm not paying the Ngai's anymore

204
00:17:38,238 --> 00:17:39,296
三位大哥的意思呢?
What do you three think?

205
00:17:50,078 --> 00:17:51,067
来 喝酒
Cheers.

206
00:18:32,983 --> 00:18:33,847
黄警官
Inspector Wong. 

207
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:34,739
怎么样?
What's up?

208
00:18:35,017 --> 00:18:36,245
你手下在国华楼下干什么呢?
<i>What are your men doing outside Wah's building?</i>

209
00:18:36,584 --> 00:18:37,573
啊 今天先不谈啊
Not a good time to chitchat.

210
00:18:37,918 --> 00:18:38,543
不要耍我啊!
<i>Are you up to something?</i> 

211
00:18:38,684 --> 00:18:40,151
行... 改天再说啊
Fine, fine. Next time.

212
00:18:44,769 --> 00:18:46,647
哇 这么热闹?
What's the occasion?

213
00:18:48,053 --> 00:18:49,680
来... 给我个位子
Come on. Where's my seat?

214
00:18:55,988 --> 00:18:58,718
你要是来吃饭 我们会很高兴
Only if you 're here for the food. Then we're cool.

215
00:18:59,322 --> 00:19:01,222
其它的事 过了今晚再说
All other business will have to wait.

216
00:19:01,522 --> 00:19:03,490
吃东西呀!吃吧
The food. It's all about the food.

217
00:19:11,014 --> 00:19:13,350
今天晚上肯定不简单
Tonight's gonna be the shit.

218
00:19:14,825 --> 00:19:16,622
没办法 等他们四个老大办完事
Let the Big Four do their things

219
00:19:16,859 --> 00:19:17,917
我们再收拾残局吧
We'll deal with the aftermath.

220
00:19:19,593 --> 00:19:21,083
这仗一打
Don't let them start fighting

221
00:19:21,459 --> 00:19:23,256
不知道死多少人
or you'll see bodies.

222
00:19:23,561 --> 00:19:25,153
怎么?不满意啊?
What? You don't dig it?

223
00:19:26,594 --> 00:19:29,688
照旧 抽牌决定
You know the rule. Pick a card.

224
00:19:30,228 --> 00:19:31,388
好呀 我们比大
Okay. Higher points win

225
00:19:31,628 --> 00:19:32,595
来呀
Come on!

226
00:19:45,965 --> 00:19:49,559
没话好说啦!还找我干什么?
There's nothing left to talk about. What do you want from me?

227
00:19:51,066 --> 00:19:52,260
怎么样 阿孝?
What's up, Hau?

228
00:19:52,732 --> 00:19:53,699
国华
Wah.

229
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:54,959
没什么
Nothing much.

230
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,566
我知道你最近在澳门谈赌场的生意
Heard you're planning a casino in Macau.

231
00:19:58,968 --> 00:20:00,833
政府方面我已经谈妥了
I've got the authorities in my pocket.

232
00:20:01,101 --> 00:20:02,762
看你有没有兴趣一起搞
How about a joint venture?

233
00:20:03,335 --> 00:20:05,030
坤叔死了
Uncle Kwun's dead.

234
00:20:05,302 --> 00:20:06,462
我什么兴趣都没有
I'm not in the mood.

235
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:12,370
那倒是
I see.

236
00:20:13,437 --> 00:20:15,735
你到澳门不只是谈生意
The Macau trip wasn't all business.

237
00:20:17,204 --> 00:20:19,968
还跟甘地的老婆玩得挺开心
I know you had fun with Gandhi's wife.

238
00:20:46,623 --> 00:20:50,236
不好意思 我澳门的赌场不能放手
Sorry, but I can't let go of my casino in Macau.

239
00:20:50,378 --> 00:20:51,310
我先走了
Gotta go.

240
00:21:12,249 --> 00:21:13,841
韩琛那帮人在搞什么?
What are Sam's people doing?

241
00:21:15,016 --> 00:21:17,007
我知道国华已经交钱了
I know Wah paid up.

242
00:21:18,317 --> 00:21:19,579
你别把话岔开
Don't change the subject.

243
00:21:19,850 --> 00:21:21,943
告诉我不知道的事 好不好?
Tell me something I don't know.

244
00:21:23,751 --> 00:21:25,218
好了 等你搞清楚再打给我
Call me when you get your shit straight!

245
00:21:27,241 --> 00:21:31,382
阿孝上去不到十分钟就搞定了国华
Hau took care of Wah in ten minutes.

246
00:21:31,653 --> 00:21:35,020
我看今晚那四个老大很难搞定他
The Big Four are having a tough time.

247
00:21:37,888 --> 00:21:40,254
我的线人说他拿了一百万毒品出来
Hau took out a million's worth of coke.

248
00:21:56,158 --> 00:21:57,125
干什么?
What?

249
00:21:57,692 --> 00:21:59,091
黑社会封路啊?
Mafia road block or what?

250
00:22:10,628 --> 00:22:13,460
倪先生 国华为何要交钱 我不知道
I don't know why Wah paid up, Hau.

251
00:22:13,461 --> 00:22:15,787
总之 我是没得商量
But I ain't gonna negotiate.

252
00:22:16,029 --> 00:22:17,291
我没打算跟你商量
I don't plan to negotiate with you, either. 

253
00:22:17,529 --> 00:22:18,553
你叫黑鬼听
Pass the phone to Negro.

254
00:22:20,096 --> 00:22:21,324
黑鬼
Hey, Negro.

255
00:22:21,930 --> 00:22:24,490
我也不晓得他为什么在我地盘打电话给你
Don't know why he calls you from my hood.

256
00:22:27,465 --> 00:22:28,454
怎么样 阿孝?
What's up, Hau?

257
00:22:29,131 --> 00:22:31,292
甘地说的就等于是我说的
I'm with Gandhi all the way.

258
00:22:32,399 --> 00:22:35,391
他不交 我也不交了
He's not paying, neitherwill I!

259
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:39,133
不要紧 听说最近你跟甘地走得挺近
Heard you and Gandhi have been tight.

260
00:22:39,433 --> 00:22:43,164
还一起运了一批海洛因 但是被人劫走了
The heroin you two smuggled got robbed.

261
00:22:43,565 --> 00:22:45,533
每人损失了几百万 对吧?
Lost several millions each, right?

262
00:22:47,165 --> 00:22:49,395
幸好 我在你的仓里捡回来
Luckily I found the stuff in your warehouse.

263
00:22:50,065 --> 00:22:51,930
要不要我现在交给甘地的小弟?
Want me to hand it back to Gandhi now?

264
00:22:55,079 --> 00:22:57,309
喂 他说什么呀?
What's he talking about?

265
00:23:12,295 --> 00:23:13,922
尖沙嘴五帮人
Among the Tsim Sha Tsui Big Fives...

266
00:23:14,095 --> 00:23:17,030
国华 黑鬼都交钱了
Wah and Negro paid up.

267
00:23:17,928 --> 00:23:19,953
加上琛哥 三比二
Counting Sam, that's 3 to 2.

268
00:23:20,861 --> 00:23:22,988
这儿我最小 不交不行
I'm the junior partner here. Gotta pay!

269
00:23:24,961 --> 00:23:26,451
二位 告辞
See ya!

270
00:23:32,594 --> 00:23:34,721
别想那么多了 干杯
Don't think too much. Cheers!

271
00:23:43,125 --> 00:23:44,490
给我把钱交了
Pay my share for me.

272
00:23:49,975 --> 00:23:52,773
黄警官 倪先生让我告诉你 他吃宵夜去了
Mr. Ngai went to get a quick bite, Inspector Wong.

273
00:24:28,803 --> 00:24:30,771
倪先生 这么晚才吃饭?
A bit late for chowing down, don't you think?

274
00:24:32,970 --> 00:24:35,768
这么多年来 爸爸习惯了来这儿吃宵夜
My dad always came here after work.

275
00:24:36,236 --> 00:24:38,830
我今晚办完事 照例来光顾一下
I have to keep up the ritual.

276
00:24:39,436 --> 00:24:41,768
怎么样 有没有兴趣?一起
Want to join us?

277
00:24:43,435 --> 00:24:45,699
看来这位子是你来坐了 辛苦了
It's your seat from now on. Must be tough.

278
00:24:46,768 --> 00:24:47,962
哪儿的话
Not at all.

279
00:24:49,002 --> 00:24:50,867
你们今晚劳师动众
You guys worked all night for nothing.

280
00:24:51,102 --> 00:24:53,570
但是一无收获 不是更辛苦?
Now that's tough.

281
00:24:55,234 --> 00:24:59,068
阿孝 你今天晚上表现真不错
Well done, Hau .

282
00:24:59,567 --> 00:25:01,159
我希望你一直这样
Hope you can keep it up.

283
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:04,362
我不想看到以后有什么事发生 走
Don't let it turn into a tragedy. Let's go.

284
00:25:04,733 --> 00:25:05,961
你不想什么?
What did you say?

285
00:25:09,332 --> 00:25:11,323
我们想开香槟庆祝
We want to celebrate.

286
00:25:11,666 --> 00:25:12,394
倪坤死了
Kwun's dead.

287
00:25:12,633 --> 00:25:14,430
我们想开香槟庆祝
Time to pop the champagne.

288
00:25:28,063 --> 00:25:29,724
要不要我给开一瓶啊?
Want me to pop one for you?

289
00:25:32,430 --> 00:25:33,282
干什么?
What?

290
00:25:33,283 --> 00:25:36,184
想干警察?
Want to mess with cops?

291
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:42,586
哎!两位警官
Officers!

292
00:25:43,362 --> 00:25:44,954
今天倪家已经少了个人
The Ngai's are in mourning,

293
00:25:45,662 --> 00:25:46,959
还想怎么样?
What more do you want?

294
00:25:51,628 --> 00:25:53,220
走吧 走
Let's go. Let's go.

295
00:26:02,593 --> 00:26:03,423
琛哥
Sam.

296
00:26:07,493 --> 00:26:08,223
谢谢
Thanks.

297
00:26:20,825 --> 00:26:22,918
爸爸以前开小赌档
Dad used to operate street gambling here.

298
00:26:24,224 --> 00:26:26,192
从几毛钱小生意
Started out as...

299
00:26:27,258 --> 00:26:28,919
做到现在
a nickel-and-dime business.

300
00:26:30,357 --> 00:26:32,689
整个尖沙嘴没有人不认识他
Now who doesn't know his name in Tsim Sha Tsui?

301
00:26:43,655 --> 00:26:45,350
他常说出来跑...
He often said...

302
00:26:46,989 --> 00:26:48,547
迟早要还
"What goes around comes around."

303
00:26:49,921 --> 00:26:51,354
想不到今天...
And now he's...

304
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,888
我会永远记住今天
I'll always remember this day.

305
00:27:45,374 --> 00:27:46,314
喂
Hello?

306
00:27:46,315 --> 00:27:49,409
老婆 没事了 要不要宵夜?
<i>Hi. honey. It's all good. Want some snacks?</i>

307
00:27:49,781 --> 00:27:52,648
没事就好 我回家等你
Good to hear that. Just come home.

308
00:28:01,946 --> 00:28:03,277
27149
27149.

309
00:28:03,813 --> 00:28:06,782
当警察的一定要身家清白
An officer has to have a clean background.

310
00:28:08,246 --> 00:28:11,773
虽然你跟母姓 多年来跟倪家没来往
Though you cut your ties with the Ngai's and changed your last name...

311
00:28:12,212 --> 00:28:15,010
但你和倪永孝到底是同一个父亲
...you still share the same father with Hau

312
00:28:15,478 --> 00:28:18,606
已经违反了虚报个人背景的校规
That means you lied on your application.

313
00:28:18,978 --> 00:28:20,605
我一定要开除你
I have to let you go.

314
00:28:21,677 --> 00:28:23,269
但你走之前
But before you leave...

315
00:28:23,911 --> 00:28:26,607
你先见一见刚才穿错袜子的那个人
...go see "Mr. Wrong Socks" first

316
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:33,634
还想不想当警察?
Still want to be a cop?

317
00:28:38,476 --> 00:28:39,773
我还可以吗?
Can I still?

318
00:28:41,508 --> 00:28:43,408
只要你给我一个好的理由
Only if you can give me a good reason.

319
00:28:47,342 --> 00:28:48,775
我想做好人
I want to be a righteous person.

320
00:29:23,137 --> 00:29:24,126
要当警察
If you want to be a cop...

321
00:29:24,371 --> 00:29:26,498
除了帮我 你没别的选择
...then lend me a hand. Simple as that

322
00:29:28,136 --> 00:29:30,297
你选我 是因为我是阿孝的弟弟?
You picked me 'cause I'm Hau 's brother, right?

323
00:29:32,603 --> 00:29:34,833
当有需要的时候 你会不会亲手捉他?
When the time comes, will you arrest him yourself?

324
00:29:36,869 --> 00:29:38,029
那我怎么开始?
How do I start?

325
00:29:40,869 --> 00:29:44,029
别吵 安静点
Shut up, Keep quiet

326
00:29:58,869 --> 00:30:00,529
你不认识我 在这儿
- You don't know me. - Over here!

327
00:30:03,135 --> 00:30:04,227
揍他!
Get him!

328
00:30:07,237 --> 00:30:09,229
揍他
Get him! Get him!

329
00:30:09,532 --> 00:30:10,362
蹲下
Brace

330
00:30:10,532 --> 00:30:12,062
哎 长官 怎么样 赛果怎么样啊?
What's the score, Officer?

331
00:30:12,532 --> 00:30:13,262
别吵
Shut up.

332
00:30:17,532 --> 00:30:19,262
哎你看 傻强啊!
Any casualties?

333
00:30:31,597 --> 00:30:32,529
还好吗?
You okay?

334
00:30:38,696 --> 00:30:39,754
挺得住吗?
Hanging in there?

335
00:31:15,968 --> 00:31:18,180
怎么样?
What's wrong?

336
00:31:18,757 --> 00:31:19,917
打得你很疼啊?
Does it still hurt?

337
00:31:21,124 --> 00:31:23,752
我老爸今天死了
My dad passed away today.

338
00:31:24,624 --> 00:31:26,785
他是最疼我的
He was so good to me.

339
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:29,583
我去求长官...
I asked the officer...

340
00:31:29,856 --> 00:31:34,190
问他能不能让我出去拜他
if I could go to his funeral.

341
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:36,917
长官就对我说...
The officer said...

342
00:31:37,456 --> 00:31:41,756
他说 "你知不知道什么叫坐牢?
"Know what it means to be a prisoner?

343
00:31:42,889 --> 00:31:47,087
"坐牢就是 就算你老爸死了
"It means you're not allowed

344
00:31:47,654 --> 00:31:50,214
"也不能让你出去拜的
"even to attend your father's funeral.

345
00:31:50,487 --> 00:31:52,284
你明不明白?"
Don't you know that?"

346
00:31:53,521 --> 00:31:55,045
走吧
Get out of here!

347
00:31:55,652 --> 00:32:08,643
哎 别这样 别哭了
Come on. Stop that

348
00:32:33,568 --> 00:32:35,934
(时间)
(Time)

349
00:32:36,934 --> 00:32:40,934
(1995年)
(Year: 1995)

350
00:33:07,346 --> 00:33:08,404
你有病?
Are you nuts?

351
00:33:09,179 --> 00:33:10,908
你派阿仁去做卧底
You sent Yan to be a mole?

352
00:33:11,345 --> 00:33:12,972
你知不知道阿孝是他亲哥哥?
Don't you know Hau's his half-brother?

353
00:33:18,078 --> 00:33:19,067
那又怎么样?
So what?

354
00:33:21,811 --> 00:33:22,937
把他资料给我
Bring me his file!

355
00:33:29,610 --> 00:33:31,510
你不是升了官就给我脸色看吧?
So you're playing the boss now, huh?

356
00:33:32,943 --> 00:33:36,470
你应该知道警队机密档案是不可以随便泄露
You damn well know the files are classified.

357
00:33:39,609 --> 00:33:42,601
我把你当兄弟 你跟我说这个?
I treat you like a bro. Is this what I get?

358
00:34:04,372 --> 00:34:06,237
你当我是兄弟就不要问
If you're a real bro, stop asking!

359
00:34:58,433 --> 00:34:59,730
没事吧
It's okay.

360
00:35:00,433 --> 00:35:01,832
冷静点
Calm down.

361
00:35:02,166 --> 00:35:03,724
慢慢说嘛
Don't lose your head.

362
00:35:04,133 --> 00:35:05,657
她把孩子打掉了
She had an abortion!

363
00:35:07,532 --> 00:35:10,524
那有什么 生孩子嘛
It's no big deal. Just a baby.

364
00:35:10,765 --> 00:35:14,098
