What's wrong with Hong Kong? Tell me!

417
00:39:44,067 --> 00:39:46,160
我记得爸爸买这儿的时候是...
When my dad bought it,

418
00:39:46,568 --> 00:39:49,867
九百...二十八万
it was 9 million...280 thousand.

419
00:39:50,267 --> 00:39:51,700
