Trading up, Mr. Ngai?

421
00:39:54,066 --> 00:39:57,126
没什么 九七了 移民
1997 is approaching. Time to emigrate.

422
00:39:58,399 --> 00:39:59,229
那有什么大不了的?
No big deal. 

423
