...among you guys

433
00:40:30,577 --> 00:40:34,980
当是感谢也好 公积金也好 对吧
Treat it as a gift or a retirement fund.

434
00:40:38,565 --> 00:40:40,897
吃啊 喜欢吃什么就拿什么
Let's eat! Take whatever you want!

435
00:40:41,707 --> 00:40:45,643
