He'll go in person next Wednesday.

469
00:43:46,246 --> 00:43:49,374
十四号 倪坤的死忌
The 14th... Kwun's memorial.

470
00:43:49,579 --> 00:43:51,103
他想收拾那四个老大
Hau wants to whack the Big Four.

471
00:43:53,813 --> 00:43:55,804
