the two foreigners are private eyes.

549
00:55:20,202 --> 00:55:23,569
喂 老公 你在哪里?
Honey! Where are you?

550
00:55:23,968 --> 00:55:25,026
我在泰国的嘛
Thailand, of course.

551
00:55:25,634 --> 00:55:26,828
你快点回来
<i>Come back right away!</i>

552
00:55:27,368 --> 00:55:28,835
神经病!我回来干什么?
Are you nuts? Why should I come back?

553
00:55:29,068 --> 00:55:30,968
你别管那么多 你快点回来
Don't ask questions! Just come back!

554
00:55:31,602 --> 00:55:32,933
阿孝要找人杀你
Hau wants you dead!

555
00:55:33,268 --> 00:55:35,202
胡说 我正帮他做事啊
Nonsense! I'm working for him as we speak!

556
00:55:36,036 --> 00:55:37,196
你听我说
Listen to me!

557
00:55:39,236 --> 00:55:42,069
倪坤...是我杀的
I'm the one who killed Kwun.

558
00:55:53,070 --> 00:55:54,162
有没有录象机?
You've got a VCR?

559
00:55:59,805 --> 00:56:00,533
好看吗?
Isn't it good?

560
00:56:02,238 --> 00:56:03,830
非常精彩
What an awesome show!

561
00:56:06,206 --> 00:56:08,231
聪明点 有事就走
Take care. Run if you have to

562
00:56:09,405 --> 00:56:10,633
阿孝有什么说的?
What did Hau say?

563
00:56:25,440 --> 00:56:26,532
- 阿琛 - 辛尼
- Sam. - Sunny!

564
00:56:27,407 --> 00:56:30,308
倪先生他让我好好的招待你
Mr. Ngai told me to take good care of you!

565
00:58:15,382 --> 00:58:17,247
我只是记得四年前...
<i>Four years ago...</i>

566
00:58:18,217 --> 00:58:20,014
是你叫我杀掉倪坤的
<i>...you told me to kill Kwun .</i>

567
00:58:22,217 --> 00:58:24,344
你什么意思?要挟我?
<i>So what? Want to blackmail me now?</i>

568
00:58:24,584 --> 00:58:25,881
我不是要挟你
<i>I'm not blackmailing you .</i>

569
00:58:27,717 --> 00:58:30,845
而是我们现两个现在 都不能回头了
<i>We simply passed the point of no return</i>

570
00:58:34,118 --> 00:58:35,915
到时候我调走所有人
<i>I'll send everybody away then .</i>

571
00:58:40,751 --> 00:58:42,343
阿伦和钟逊
I hired Alan and Johnson...

572
00:58:43,219 --> 00:58:47,656
是我特地请来帮我查 杀我爸爸的凶手
...to investigate my father's murder

573
00:58:57,587 --> 00:59:00,021
想不到你们有些警务人员...
Who would've known? The police conspired...

574
00:59:00,488 --> 00:59:01,978
知法犯法
to murder my father.

575
00:59:03,186 --> 00:59:05,950
杀害我爸爸这样的良好市民
A law-abiding citizen.

576
00:59:09,321 --> 00:59:10,481
陆长官
SP Luk

577
00:59:12,321 --> 00:59:14,516
画面里那个 算不算警察?
Isn't that an officer in the video?

578
00:59:34,789 --> 00:59:38,225
怎么样做 抓不抓他...
Whether to nail him or not...

579
00:59:38,823 --> 00:59:40,085
你自己决定
...that's up to you

580
01:00:31,728 --> 01:00:33,127
真的很好看
What a good show!

581
01:00:38,728 --> 01:00:39,854
你很上镜
You're so friggin' photogenic.

582
01:01:15,432 --> 01:01:16,797
四年前
Four years ago...

583
01:01:17,500 --> 01:01:20,966
你们收了韩琛的女人多少钱?
How much did Sam's woman pay you?

584
01:01:24,768 --> 01:01:26,736
倪先生 给次机会吧
Give me another chance, Mr. Ngai.

585
01:01:59,927 --> 01:02:02,589
四年前 我给过他们机会
I gave them a chance four years ago.

586
01:02:02,647 --> 01:02:04,556
他们没要
They didn't take it.

587
01:02:07,192 --> 01:02:09,422
如果今天我给你机会
If I give you a chance...

588
01:02:11,558 --> 01:02:13,082
你要不要?
Are you going to take it today?

589
01:02:27,620 --> 01:02:29,417
你来了我们倪家七年
You've been with us for seven years now.

590
01:02:30,986 --> 01:02:32,214
你是警察
You're a cop.

591
01:02:36,185 --> 01:02:37,948
我们是黑社会
We're the bad guys.

592
01:02:38,693 --> 01:02:40,275
所以各安天命
Time to accept our fates.

593
01:02:45,650 --> 01:02:47,015
你不要怪我
You can't blame me.

594
01:02:48,183 --> 01:02:51,550
因为你们的黄长官杀了我爸爸
Your Inspector Wong killed my dad.

595
01:05:35,645 --> 01:05:37,442
有没有琛哥的消息?
Any words from Sam?

596
01:05:39,145 --> 01:05:40,669
琛哥联络过我
Sam called me.

597
01:05:40,910 --> 01:05:41,968
他说他没事
He said he was fine.

598
01:05:42,643 --> 01:05:46,238
叫你在这儿躲几天 等他回来
He asked you to wait for him here.

599
01:05:55,607 --> 01:05:56,767
你的家人呢?
Where are your folks?

600
01:05:58,607 --> 01:05:59,539
都移民了
All emigrated.

601
01:06:03,039 --> 01:06:04,063
你怎么不去?
You didn't go with them?

602
01:06:37,664 --> 01:06:39,063
琛哥快走!泰国人没追来
Let's go, Sam! We got rid of the Thais

603
01:06:39,264 --> 01:06:40,526
快走啊
Let's go!

604
01:06:42,697 --> 01:06:45,461
你知道你走不了的
You know you're not going to make it.

605
01:06:45,963 --> 01:06:47,021
我知道
I know.

606
01:06:48,928 --> 01:06:50,896
我女人在香港很危险
My girl's in danger in Hong Kong too.

607
01:06:52,461 --> 01:06:53,723
我求你帮帮我
Please help me.

608
01:06:54,028 --> 01:06:55,723
我为什么要帮你?
Why should I?

609
01:06:56,727 --> 01:06:58,695
因为我帮你除掉你老大
'Cause I'll help you whack your boss.

610
01:07:00,292 --> 01:07:02,453
我知道你很想坐那个位子
I know you want to be in charge.

611
01:07:04,392 --> 01:07:05,791
还有
Moreover...

612
01:07:28,286 --> 01:07:30,652
我一直当你是我的好朋友
I've been treating you as a pal.

613
01:07:36,785 --> 01:07:38,514
别信他!琛哥 别信他
Don't believe him, Sam! Don't!

614
01:07:38,695 --> 01:07:40,080
走开
Get lost!

615
01:07:40,283 --> 01:07:41,910
- 别信他 - 走开
- Don't believe him! - Get lost!

616
01:08:00,346 --> 01:08:01,438
对不起 琛哥
Sorry, Sam.

617
01:09:18,578 --> 01:09:19,875
来抓我?
Are you here to arrest me?

618
01:09:20,612 --> 01:09:22,273
你现在要去杀阿孝
If you're going to kill Hau, 

619
01:09:23,211 --> 01:09:24,405
我就抓你
I will.

620
01:09:27,743 --> 01:09:29,210
那就是没商量了
Then there's nothing to talk about.

621
01:09:33,342 --> 01:09:35,358
我跟上头已经说好了
I spoke with my superiors.

622
01:09:35,875 --> 01:09:38,503
他们说这一次 一定支持你
They're with you all the way this time.

623
01:09:39,274 --> 01:09:40,366
怎样支持?
How?

624
01:09:40,640 --> 01:09:42,005
我教唆杀人呀
I conspired in murder!

625
01:09:48,306 --> 01:09:50,399
就连上面那些老外都说
Even the Brits agree that...

626
01:09:50,805 --> 01:09:53,035
不可以让黑社会胡来
...we can't let the triads break us

627
01:09:53,609 --> 01:09:58,169
全警局的人都支持你
The whole department's behind you.

628
01:09:58,170 --> 01:09:59,797
你说够不够招?
Good enough?

629
01:10:03,269 --> 01:10:03,997
你的牌呢?
Where's your deck of cards?

630
01:10:12,400 --> 01:10:13,697
这次我们比大
The higher points win

631
01:10:16,066 --> 01:10:18,227
听我的 跟我回警局开会
I'm calling the shots. Come back with me to the department.

632
01:10:21,831 --> 01:10:22,855
钥匙
The key!

633
01:10:24,830 --> 01:10:26,229
算了 我已经够糗的了
Forget it. I screwed up.

634
01:10:26,463 --> 01:10:27,725
别连累人家了
No need to drag everyone down with me.

635
01:10:47,759 --> 01:10:49,750
这是我们第一次合作抓老千
We found this deck on our first outing together.

636
01:10:49,991 --> 01:10:51,185
你留下来的
You've been keeping it all this time.

637
01:10:51,492 --> 01:10:52,857
我一直都知道
I knew that all along.

638
01:10:54,591 --> 01:11:00,088
这么多年 我听了你好几次
I've let you get your way in the past.

639
01:11:00,089 --> 01:11:01,454
也该听我一次了吧
It's your turn to listen for once.

640
01:11:02,455 --> 01:11:04,183
我说过我们是兄弟
We're like brothers.

641
01:11:04,422 --> 01:11:06,616
你有事我能不管吗?
Think I'm just gonna be a spectator?

642
01:11:12,520 --> 01:11:14,715
罗继是我安插进去的卧底
Law's my snitch in the Ngai Family.

643
01:11:16,919 --> 01:11:18,682
已经好几天没跟我联络了
He hasn't contacted me for days.

644
01:11:20,585 --> 01:11:21,711
阿仁也是
Neither has Yan.

645
01:11:24,118 --> 01:11:25,085
钥匙
The key!

646
01:12:11,440 --> 01:12:12,464
出来呀
Help!

647
01:12:13,007 --> 01:12:14,941
帮忙啊
Help! Get some help!

648
01:12:18,691 --> 01:12:20,386
为什么?
Why?Why?

649
01:13:57,583 --> 01:13:58,515
你为什么骗我?
Why did you lie to me?

650
01:14:00,983 --> 01:14:02,041
没有啊
I didn't!

651
01:14:02,982 --> 01:14:04,415
琛哥出事了
Something happened to Sam!

652
01:14:05,781 --> 01:14:08,181
我跟你说过 我是个很简单的女人
I told you I was a simple woman.

653
01:14:08,414 --> 01:14:10,644
现在我老公出事了 我怎么也得做点事情
I have to do something for my husband.

654
01:14:11,580 --> 01:14:12,740
我要去泰国
I'm going to Thailand.

655
01:14:13,779 --> 01:14:15,144
你不去行不行?
Please don't go!

656
01:14:16,746 --> 01:14:19,544
算了 你就当没有跟过我们
Forget it! You don't have to follow us anymore

657
01:14:21,211 --> 01:14:23,839
我是说 我叫你别去行不行?
I mean, I don't want you to go.

658
01:14:29,476 --> 01:14:32,707
其实 你跟琛哥那么多年
You've been with Sam for years...

659
01:14:33,942 --> 01:14:35,375
有没有想过
Has it occurred to you...

660
01:14:37,141 --> 01:14:38,574
琛哥已经死了
Maybe Sam's dead!

661
01:14:38,741 --> 01:14:39,708
你说什么?
What did you say?

662
01:14:40,374 --> 01:14:41,306
我可以照顾你
I can take care of you.

663
01:14:47,872 --> 01:14:48,804
你干什么?
What are you doing?

664
01:14:49,138 --> 01:14:50,127
我不想你走
I don't want you to go.

665
01:14:53,238 --> 01:14:54,136
你造反啊你?
You're out of line!

666
01:15:02,569 --> 01:15:03,934
我告诉你
Listen up!

667
01:15:04,702 --> 01:15:06,329
我是你老大的女人
I'm your boss's woman!

668
01:15:11,967 --> 01:15:13,195
以后别再让我见到你
Don't let me see your face again!

669
01:16:08,254 --> 01:16:10,051
今晚她会去机场
She will go to the airport tonight...

670
01:16:10,254 --> 01:16:12,154
喂?喂?
<i>Hello? Hello?</i>

671
01:17:39,400 --> 01:17:41,129
倪坤 是我杀的
<i>I'm the one who killed Kwun.</i>

672
01:17:42,106 --> 01:17:43,437
只要男人好
<i>Aman treats me well.</i>

673
01:17:43,711 --> 01:17:44,871
我做什么都行
<i>I'd do anything.</i>

674
01:18:29,282 --> 01:18:31,807
(时间)
(Time)

675
01:18:32,807 --> 01:18:36,807
(1997年)
(Year: 1997)

676
01:18:37,693 --> 01:18:40,218
档案编号IO3142
File number IO3142

677
01:18:40,534 --> 01:18:43,594
有关黄志诚督察教唆谋杀案
About Inspector Wong conspiring in murder.

678
01:18:44,177 --> 01:18:48,011
现由三位高级警官 作第十一次内部聆讯
This is the 11 th internal hearing.

679
01:18:48,889 --> 01:18:50,186
黄志诚督察
Inspector Wong,

680
01:18:50,628 --> 01:18:51,890
你有没有问题?
do you have any questions?

681
01:18:52,867 --> 01:18:54,027
没有...
No...

682
01:18:54,372 --> 01:18:55,430
没有
No.

683
01:18:56,110 --> 01:18:59,136
身为督察 必须具备领导才能
An inspector should possess leadership skills

684
01:18:59,351 --> 01:18:59,976
刘警官
Mr. Lau

685
01:19:00,187 --> 01:19:01,586
你现为普通警员
you joined as a police constable

686
01:19:01,825 --> 01:19:03,224
能不能告诉评选会
Could you tell the promotion board

687
01:19:03,463 --> 01:19:05,431
提升你为督察的理由呢?
why you deserve to be promoted?

688
01:19:05,635 --> 01:19:06,533
当然可以
Of course

689
01:19:06,906 --> 01:19:09,841
一九九五年四月十一日
On April 11, 1995,

690
01:19:10,382 --> 01:19:13,044
投诉科收到这盒带子
The department received this tape

691
01:19:13,958 --> 01:19:17,257
指控你串谋黑帮 合谋杀人
accusing you of conspiring with the triads in a murder.

692
01:19:17,501 --> 01:19:18,695
我认罪 长官
I confess, sir.

693
01:19:19,039 --> 01:19:20,336
现在是一九九七年了
It's already 1997

694
01:19:20,576 --> 01:19:21,508
七月一号之前
If we don't receive your PO assessment report

695
01:19:21,779 --> 01:19:23,804
如果我们还没有收到你的评审报告
Before the 1st of July

696
01:19:24,086 --> 01:19:25,610
你认为还可以获得晋升吗?
Do you still think you can be promoted?

697
01:19:25,857 --> 01:19:27,381
中国人有句话
In Chinese, there is a saying

698
01:19:27,696 --> 01:19:29,994
那就是 一朝天子一朝臣
With a new king come new followers

699
01:19:30,203 --> 01:19:33,297
所以 我认为到那个时候我要重新开始
So, I guess we will have to start all over again

700
01:19:34,147 --> 01:19:35,739
你为什么会变成这样?
What happened to you?

701
01:19:38,458 --> 01:19:39,925
如果我告诉你
If I told you...

702
01:19:40,263 --> 01:19:43,255
这些所谓的证据全都不成立
...that the evidence couldn't stand...

703
01:19:45,009 --> 01:19:46,408
你想不想重新再来?
...would you like to start over?

704
01:19:49,622 --> 01:19:52,819
对不起 我犯了法
I'm sorry. I broke the law.

705
01:19:53,466 --> 01:19:56,526
你对九七以后警队的士气有什么看法?
What do you think of the police force's morale after 1997?

706
01:19:57,210 --> 01:19:59,201
中国人注重感情
Chinese people are sentimental

707
01:19:59,482 --> 01:20:01,575
我也希望法律能继续支持我
I hope the law will continue to back me up

708
01:20:01,889 --> 01:20:05,916
但是 我同样坚信自己的能力 长官
But, I strongly believe in myself, sir!

709
01:20:06,569 --> 01:20:08,400
各位怎样对我 我知道
I'm grateful to all of you.

710
01:20:10,111 --> 01:20:13,205
但我没有信心 我已经输了
But I've got no confidence left. I lost!

711
01:20:13,521 --> 01:20:14,818
那阿昌又怎样?
What about Luk then?

712
01:20:16,027 --> 01:20:18,222
你觉得现在这么做 对得起阿昌吗?
Can you face him if you give up now?

713
01:20:19,437 --> 01:20:22,406
阿黄 这场仗还没打完
The war's not over.

714
01:20:23,949 --> 01:20:27,749
我们每个人 都希望对这件事有个交待
We all want a closure to this incident.

715
01:20:29,598 --> 01:20:33,625
我们想外面知道 香港不是由姓倪的来管
Hong Kong is not run by the Ngai Family.

716
01:20:39,625 --> 01:20:41,650
这里有一份国际刑警档案
Here's a file from the Interpol.

717
01:20:42,165 --> 01:20:43,427
你看完了再作决定
Read it before your make up your mind.

718
01:21:06,000 --> 01:21:07,490
有没有参加过泰国的丧礼?
Ever been to a funeral in Thailand?

719
01:21:10,901 --> 01:21:12,334
几个月前
A few months ago...

720
01:21:13,268 --> 01:21:14,860
我为老婆办了一个
I had one for my wife.

721
01:21:16,867 --> 01:21:21,031
请了些大师 给她念了三天的经
The monks chanted for three full days.

722
01:21:24,335 --> 01:21:28,237
这三天 我没流过一滴眼泪
During those three days, I didn't shed a single tear.

723
01:21:31,570 --> 01:21:33,265
没想到出殡那天
On the day of the burial...

724
01:21:35,204 --> 01:21:39,368
那些苦力 把棺材抬到厅里
...they left the casket in the living room.

725
01:21:41,071 --> 01:21:42,299
当时我很生气
I was mad.

726
01:21:43,072 --> 01:21:44,471
很想打人
I wanted to beat them up.

727
01:21:46,706 --> 01:21:48,571
但大师就对我说
The monk told me...

728
01:21:51,173 --> 01:21:53,004
这是他们的习俗
...it's a tradition in Thailand.

729
01:21:55,339 --> 01:21:56,772
死的人
The deceased...

730
01:21:58,074 --> 01:21:59,871
只要我们能够陪她
...as long as we keep her company...

731
01:22:00,907 --> 01:22:02,841
过一段时间
...for a little while longer...

732
01:22:04,708 --> 01:22:06,699
她就可以安息了
...she can attain eternal peace.

733
01:22:11,575 --> 01:22:12,974
但是我对大师说
But I asked the monk...

734
01:22:16,576 --> 01:22:18,976
我老婆不在棺材里
...what if my wife was not in the coffin?

735
01:22:20,910 --> 01:22:22,571
她可不可以安息呀?
Could she still attain eternal peace?

736
01:22:30,278 --> 01:22:32,644
嫂子的事 对不起
Sorry about your wife.

737
01:22:39,579 --> 01:22:41,809
大师马上按住我这里
The monk placed his hand here.

738
01:22:43,380 --> 01:22:45,610
他说 "没问题
He said, "No problem,

739
01:22:47,780 --> 01:22:50,214
你太太在你这儿就行喽"
Your wife's here."

740
01:22:56,315 --> 01:22:58,112
而碰巧这里
And here's exactly...

741
01:23:00,716 --> 01:23:03,276
就是泰国人打我一枪的地方
...where the Thais shot me!

742
01:23:07,583 --> 01:23:09,517
我立刻对自己说
So I told myself,

743
01:23:15,951 --> 01:23:18,112
我是不可能再回头了
I've passed the point of no return.

744
01:23:23,218 --> 01:23:27,518
这次回香港指证倪永孝 很危险
Testifying against Hau in Hong Kong could be dangerous.

745
01:23:32,352 --> 01:23:35,185
你这么帅 我有信心
I believe in you . You 're so handsome.

746
01:23:39,154 --> 01:23:41,884
很久没人跟我说这句话了 谢谢
Haven't heard that for ages. Thanks.

747
01:23:45,121 --> 01:23:46,179
你有什么打算?
What's your plan?

748
01:23:49,389 --> 01:23:50,788
尽力而为吧
Just trying to do my best.

749
01:23:51,556 --> 01:23:53,421
没什么 工作嘛
No big deal. It's my job.

750
01:23:55,256 --> 01:23:58,191
搞定这件事之后 我会离开香港
I'll leave Hong Kong when it's all over.

751
01:24:06,556 --> 01:24:08,475
阿黄
Hey,you!

752
01:24:26,894 --> 01:24:28,054
你变了
You've changed.

753
01:24:33,762 --> 01:24:34,786
宝宝
Baby!

754
01:25:21,317 --> 01:25:22,716
货里掺东西了?
You diluted the coke, didn't you?

755
01:25:26,352 --> 01:25:27,580
没话说了?
Got anything to say?

756
01:25:42,320 --> 01:25:43,446
全给我吸了它
Take it all then.

757
01:25:49,255 --> 01:25:51,416
阿仁 别那么绝
Don't go too far, Yan.

758
01:25:51,689 --> 01:25:53,657
让小的看见 哪有心情做事啊?
It'd break the boys' morale.

759
01:25:57,556 --> 01:25:59,581
倪先生叫我这么做的
Mr. Ngai asked me to be in charge here.

760
01:26:01,157 --> 01:26:03,352
不喜欢就送他上医院
Don't like it? Drive him to the hospital!

761
01:26:18,893 --> 01:26:20,383
无论他们做错什么
No matter what,

762
01:26:20,626 --> 01:26:22,059
他们始终是长辈
they're elders after all.

763
01:26:23,627 --> 01:26:25,686
你以后还有很多东西要跟他们学
You 've got lots to learn from them.

764
01:26:27,994 --> 01:26:30,758
三叔再做几年就退休了
Uncle John will retire in a few years.

765
01:26:33,561 --> 01:26:34,755
你明白我的意思吧?
You know what I mean?

766
01:26:36,828 --> 01:26:39,762
我不想在这个时候 有什么事情发生
I don't need any hiccups now.

767
01:26:42,662 --> 01:26:45,688
今晚劳工体育会请吃回归宴
The Labor Athletic Association is hosting a dinner reception...

768
01:26:46,563 --> 01:26:49,123
我们所有的政协候选人都会去
...for us Political Consultative candidates.

769
01:26:50,431 --> 01:26:52,228
如果这次我成功
If everything works out,

770
01:26:53,497 --> 01:26:55,658
我们倪家以后就能抬起头来做人
our family will no longer live in the shadows.

771
01:27:23,168 --> 01:27:24,066
张先生
Mr. Cheung.

772
01:27:24,301 --> 01:27:25,199
- 倪先生 - 总会主席
- Mr. Ngai - Chairman

773
01:27:25,735 --> 01:27:27,327
- 你好 - 你好...
- How are you? - Good. Good

774
01:27:27,601 --> 01:27:29,364
我听洪大律师提起过你呀
When Solicitor Hung mentioned you,

775
01:27:29,568 --> 01:27:30,933
我还不大相信呢
I didn't believe him.

776
01:27:31,803 --> 01:27:34,636
倪先生 你看看你 你真是年青有为啊
You 're amazingly young, Mr. Ngai.

777
01:27:34,969 --> 01:27:35,731
属啥的?
What's your Zodiac sign?

778
01:27:37,336 --> 01:27:38,064
牛
Ox.

779
01:27:38,304 --> 01:27:39,236
属牛
The Year of the Ox.

780
01:27:39,670 --> 01:27:41,297
属牛好啊
Ox is good.

781
01:27:42,004 --> 01:27:44,905
陈主任最喜欢跟年轻人打交道
Director Chan likes young people.

782
01:27:45,070 --> 01:27:46,935
- 待会儿给你介绍介绍 - 谢谢
- I'll introduce you later. - Thanks.

783
01:27:47,271 --> 01:27:48,169
是吗?
Really?

784
01:27:50,439 --> 01:27:54,705
主任对我说过 他是最痛恨黑社会的
Director Chan said he hated the triads.

785
01:28:01,007 --> 01:28:02,406
对了 梁长官
That's right, SP Leung

786
01:28:03,307 --> 01:28:06,799
倪先生刚接受邀请 到警察投诉部当顾问
Mr. Ngai's been invited to consult with the police.

787
01:28:07,073 --> 01:28:09,473
是吗?恭喜恭喜呀
Really? Congratulations!

788
01:28:09,641 --> 01:28:11,506
老陈 最近到哪里打球?
Where do you golf these days, Chan?

789
01:28:11,707 --> 01:28:12,196
中山
Zhong Shan Onsen

790
01:28:12,475 --> 01:28:14,739
中山?你现在打多少杆哪?
Zhong Shan? What's your handicap these days?

791
01:28:15,008 --> 01:28:19,075
你好你好 小姓倪
How are you? My name's Ngai...

792
01:28:27,043 --> 01:28:28,135
倪永孝先生
Mr. Ngai Wing-Hau.

793
01:28:32,111 --> 01:28:33,339
我是倪先生律师
I'm Mr. Ngai's solicitor.

794
01:28:33,645 --> 01:28:36,170
今天是劳工体育会的回归酒会
Tonight's a celebration for HK's hand-over.

795
01:28:36,478 --> 01:28:37,945
有什么事 酒会之后再说行吗?
All other business can wait.

796
01:28:38,178 --> 01:28:39,304
我说不行
What if I say no?

797
01:28:39,812 --> 01:28:40,779
有没有问题?
Got any problem with that?

798
01:28:44,613 --> 01:28:45,637
倪先生
Mr. Ngai, 

799
01:28:45,913 --> 01:28:46,379
现在怀疑你
You're a suspect

800
01:28:46,679 --> 01:28:49,170
和一九九五年多宗谋杀案有关
in several murder cases in 1995.

801
01:28:50,680 --> 01:28:51,908
这张是拘捕令
You're under arrest

802
01:28:52,380 --> 01:28:53,608
现在要拘捕你
This is your arrest warrant

803
01:28:54,246 --> 01:28:55,406
你所说的话
Everything you say

804
01:28:55,748 --> 01:28:57,340
我们会用纸和笔记下
will be recorded...

805
01:28:57,481 --> 01:28:59,278
将来作为呈堂证供
and could be used as evidence against you.

806
01:28:59,615 --> 01:29:00,343
有没有问题?
Do you have any questions?

807
01:29:01,348 --> 01:29:02,076
没有
No.

808
01:29:16,150 --> 01:29:17,208
我看过他们的资料
I looked through their files.

809
01:29:17,750 --> 01:29:19,274
谋杀罪名一定不成立
The murder charges won't stand.

810
01:29:20,150 --> 01:29:22,584
不过 身为三合会的龙头
But your being a triad boss...

811
01:29:23,051 --> 01:29:24,609
我无法帮你脱罪
That one will stick.

812
01:29:25,618 --> 01:29:28,519
三哥 刚才几个工会和政党打电话来
The unions and the political parties called.

813
01:29:28,819 --> 01:29:30,719
说想收回他们回归晚会的贴子
They want to withdraw their invitations.

814
01:29:34,085 --> 01:29:35,712
港奥办来消息
Words from the HK and Macau Affairs Office

815
01:29:36,419 --> 01:29:38,148
你候选人的资格被取消了
They have revoked your candidacy.

816
01:29:38,887 --> 01:29:41,253
打电话去北京 找些朋友帮忙
Call Beijing. Get some friends to help.

817
01:29:41,687 --> 01:29:42,619
我试试看
Let me try.

818
01:29:42,921 --> 01:29:43,945
算了
Forget it.

819
01:29:44,420 --> 01:29:46,411
他们连个死了的人都能找到
They even found a dead man to testify against you.

820
01:29:46,922 --> 01:29:49,447
所有人都知道 韩琛对倪家忠心耿耿
Everyone knows how loyal Sam was to you.

821
01:29:49,922 --> 01:29:51,913
他做污点证人 这官司怎么打?
Now he's a prosecution witness. It's over.

822
01:29:52,922 --> 01:29:54,389
对不起 我帮不了你
Sorry. Can't help you.

823
01:29:55,422 --> 01:29:56,912
那时候 你说可以顺利过渡
You said there'd be no problem.

824
01:29:57,556 --> 01:29:59,353
大家都看好我们倪家
Everyone's watching how we will react.

825
01:29:59,590 --> 01:30:00,784
现在怎么办?
What're you going to do?

826
01:30:01,523 --> 01:30:02,683
你要我怎么办?
What can I do?

827
01:30:02,856 --> 01:30:03,788
恐吓中国政府啊?
Threaten the Chinese government?

828
01:30:04,023 --> 01:30:05,354
他不是这个意思
Don't take it the wrong way.

829
01:30:05,723 --> 01:30:07,554
只不过大家同坐一条船
We're all in the same boat.

830
01:30:07,924 --> 01:30:09,050
那我下船了
Time for me to get off then

831
01:30:10,025 --> 01:30:12,323
我是你们的律师 不是你们的人
I'm just a lawyer. Not one of you.

832
01:30:12,925 --> 01:30:16,051
我不想跟你们沉船 对不起
I don't intend to sink with you . Sorry.

833
01:30:26,960 --> 01:30:27,984
是
Yes.

834
01:30:29,227 --> 01:30:31,787
查到韩琛有个老婆和女儿在泰国
Sam has a wife and daughter in Thailand.

835
01:30:33,727 --> 01:30:35,058
怎么做你看着办
It's your call.

836
01:30:42,662 --> 01:30:43,720
姐
Sis.

837
01:30:45,162 --> 01:30:47,528
我想你和大哥 弟弟陪妈妈
You and the brothers should take mom...

838
01:30:47,763 --> 01:30:49,492
去夏威夷那边住一段时间
... and go to Hawaii for a while.

839
01:30:50,763 --> 01:30:51,492
好吧
Yes.

840
01:30:51,996 --> 01:30:54,590
也好 反正我们很久没过去了
Okay. Haven't been there for a while.

841
01:31:04,998 --> 01:31:06,363
你会不会有事?
Are you going to be all right?

842
01:31:06,599 --> 01:31:07,930
没事...
I'll be fine.

843
01:31:09,132 --> 01:31:11,225
对不起 我帮不上家里什么忙
Sorry I can't help the family.

844
01:31:11,732 --> 01:31:12,630
最要紧你没事
The key thing now is you turn out okay.

845
01:31:12,866 --> 01:31:14,197
别这么说 一家人嘛
Don't be silly. We're a family.

846
01:31:15,233 --> 01:31:16,666
照顾妈妈
Take care of mom!

847
01:31:17,100 --> 01:31:19,034
放心 交给我们三个
Don't worry. Leave it to us three.

848
01:31:30,686 --> 01:31:33,746
我总觉得 就算我出庭作证
Even with my testimony,

849
01:31:35,600 --> 01:31:38,615
阿孝顶多坐几年牢而已
Hau will only get a couple years.

850
01:31:39,434 --> 01:31:40,934
那倒是
It's true.

851
01:31:40,935 --> 01:31:44,751
如果要他终身监禁 除非他杀了你
He'll have to whack you to get life.

852
01:31:48,935 --> 01:31:49,763
- 我走了 - 阿黄
- I Gotta go - Hey, you

853
01:31:52,105 --> 01:31:54,237
这次真的谢谢你
I have to thank you.

854
01:31:54,238 --> 01:31:55,708
没有你
Without you

855
01:31:56,042 --> 01:31:57,441
我也回不了香港
I could never have come back to Hong Kong.

856
01:32:00,907 --> 01:32:03,374
不跟你说了 我最近很忙
Save it! I'm busy these days.

857
01:32:03,375 --> 01:32:05,941
你有什么需要 就跟他们说
Anything you need, ask them.

858
01:32:05,942 --> 01:32:08,069
这组人负责保护你
They'll protect you.

859
01:32:08,106 --> 01:32:09,403
行!
I know.

860
01:32:24,847 --> 01:32:26,896
琛哥
Sam.

861
01:32:29,549 --> 01:32:31,762
谢谢
Thanks.

862
01:32:33,550 --> 01:32:36,049
怎么样 好吗?
So, how's it going?

863
01:32:36,050 --> 01:32:39,551
还好 调到刑事情报科
Good. Been transferred to the ClB.

864
01:32:39,552 --> 01:32:42,556
下个月升做见习督察
I'll be an Inspector-in-Training next month.

865
01:32:47,987 --> 01:32:50,381
玛莉姐走的时候
Did Mary call you...

866
01:32:50,855 --> 01:32:53,476
有没有找过你?
...before she left?

867
01:33:00,524 --> 01:33:04,213
琛哥 节哀顺变
Don't be too hard on yourself, Sam.

868
01:33:09,661 --> 01:33:14,869
黄长官说 有什么事可以找你
Inspector Wong said to find you if I needed anything.

869
01:33:17,229 --> 01:33:20,133
你是不是真的会帮我?
Will you really help me?

870
01:34:32,484 --> 01:34:33,849
我以为你不会来
I thought you wouldn't come.

871
01:34:37,118 --> 01:34:39,090
为什么我不会来?
Why's that?

872
01:34:54,757 --> 01:34:56,856
怎么样?
So here we are.

873
01:34:56,857 --> 01:34:58,905
两年了
It's been two years.

874
01:35:00,159 --> 01:35:02,093
因为有份杀我爸爸
Because of my father's case,

875
01:35:02,392 --> 01:35:04,019
所以两年都不敢找我?
you didn't dare to call me for two years?

876
01:35:04,493 --> 01:35:05,824
不敢跟我说话?
You couldn't face me?

877
01:35:08,695 --> 01:35:10,471
是
Right.

878
01:35:20,497 --> 01:35:24,297
保险箱里 是倪家这两年的犯罪证据
All you need to nail Hau is in the safe.

879
01:35:25,800 --> 01:35:28,358
我排好档案和日期了
I've organized the files according to date.

880
01:35:32,501 --> 01:35:33,763
为什么还肯帮我?
Why do you still help me?

881
01:35:42,438 --> 01:35:44,619
我不是想帮你
I'm not helping you.

882
01:35:46,305 --> 01:35:47,636
我是警察
I'm a cop.

883
01:35:48,806 --> 01:35:51,686
我答应过陆长官的事 我要做到
I want to keep my promises to SP Luk!

884
01:35:54,174 --> 01:35:55,869
我不想再做卧底了
And I don't want to be a mole anymore.

885
01:35:58,009 --> 01:36:00,773
再做两年 我就成尖沙嘴老大了
Two more years and I'll become the top dog in Tsim Sha Tsui.

886
01:36:02,010 --> 01:36:04,979
怎么办?想坐牢啊?
What for? To end up in prison?

887
01:36:13,080 --> 01:36:14,775
以前的事我忘了
Let's bury the past.

888
01:36:15,814 --> 01:36:19,181
总之拜托你赶快办完这件事 调我回警署
Just finish up my case and bring me back into the department.

889
01:36:20,349 --> 01:36:22,442
给我一个平平稳稳的位子
Give me a decent desk.

890
01:36:23,249 --> 01:36:25,430
要对着海
Make sure it has a sea view.

891
01:36:26,817 --> 01:36:29,165
但是别再让我再见到你
And don't let me see your face again.

892
01:36:32,151 --> 01:36:32,845
放心吧
Don't worry.

893
01:36:33,152 --> 01:36:34,585
你不会见到我
You won't see me anymore.

894
01:36:35,820 --> 01:36:36,650
还有
One more thing.

895
01:36:38,587 --> 01:36:40,521
档案里有些字我不会写
I couldn't spell some of the words.

896
01:36:40,821 --> 01:36:42,118
你看不懂就来找我
Come find me if you don't understand.

897
01:36:43,222 --> 01:36:46,680
但千万别调乱了次序 我排了很久
But don't mess up the order.

898
01:36:47,190 --> 01:36:48,384
调乱了 我宰了你
I'll kill you if you mess that up.

899
01:36:50,191 --> 01:36:52,352
那就好了 债可以还清了
That's great. Put me out of misery.

900
01:36:53,058 --> 01:36:55,913
想得美
You wish.

901
01:37:02,828 --> 01:37:03,886
谢谢警官
Thank you, Officer.

902
01:38:08,029 --> 01:38:10,896
阿琛 资料齐了 律政司批示三天后上庭
Sum, we're all set. The trial will start in three days.

903
01:38:12,698 --> 01:38:13,665
韩先生
Mr. Han

904
01:39:13,681 --> 01:39:14,648
重案组
Hello, OCTB!

905
01:39:17,949 --> 01:39:20,417
黄长官 证人不见了
Inspector Wong! Sam's gone!

906
01:39:35,388 --> 01:39:37,322
韩琛应该是从厨房通道跑掉的
He escaped through the kitchen.

907
01:39:37,655 --> 01:39:39,122
谁把守厨房通道?
Who was guarding the kitchen?

908
01:39:42,990 --> 01:39:43,888
对不起 长官
Sorry, sir.

909
01:39:45,691 --> 01:39:47,750
黄长官 韩琛走之前
Officer Wong, Sam'd made a call to Thailand...

910
01:39:48,025 --> 01:39:49,424
打了个电话回泰国
...before he escaped

911
01:39:53,191 --> 01:39:54,180
喂
Hello?

912
01:40:44,108 --> 01:40:45,040
倪先生
Mr. Ngai.

913
01:40:46,008 --> 01:40:47,373
找我什么事啊?
What do you want from me?

914
01:40:49,275 --> 01:40:50,708
是你打话给我的
You called me.

915
01:40:52,110 --> 01:40:55,273
所以应该你告诉我 能帮我什么忙
So tell me how you can help me.

916
01:40:55,578 --> 01:40:57,512
对吧?坐
Am I right? Sit down.

917
01:41:08,782 --> 01:41:10,079
杀我吧
Kill me.

918
01:41:13,282 --> 01:41:14,943
杀了我就天下太平了
Kill me and it's all over.

919
01:41:15,917 --> 01:41:17,282
我为什么要杀你?
Why should I?

920
01:41:17,751 --> 01:41:19,275
我没干这种事很久了
Haven't done that kind of stuff for ages.

921
01:41:23,085 --> 01:41:25,645
有什么话 可以坐下来慢慢商量
Everything can be negotiated, Sam.

922
01:41:26,020 --> 01:41:27,953
香港这么大
Hong Kong's big enough for us both, Sam.

923
01:41:27,954 --> 01:41:31,507
你愿意的话 我们可以一起合作
We can even be partners.

924
01:41:35,256 --> 01:41:36,689
以前的事算了
Let's forget about the past.

925
01:41:53,161 --> 01:41:54,788
你一定会杀我
You will kill me.

926
01:41:56,329 --> 01:41:57,956
今晚你就会杀我
You 'll kill me tonight.

927
01:42:09,166 --> 01:42:11,760
我杀了你 你老婆和女儿怎么办?
But who's gonna take care of your family?

928
01:42:30,305 --> 01:42:31,237
刚刚收到消息
Just in!

929
01:42:31,506 --> 01:42:33,974
倪永孝抓了韩琛在泰国的老婆和女儿
Hau has Sam's wife and daughter as hostages.

930
01:42:34,906 --> 01:42:37,204
那是他泰国的佣人
That's his Thai maid.

931
01:42:46,543 --> 01:42:49,637
这几年 我死不了
I managed to stay alive all these years.

932
